# streaming.bl — Streaming Large Files
# Tutorial: https://lang.bio/docs/tutorials/streaming.html
#
# Run with: bl run examples/tutorials/streaming.bl
#
# Note: Most examples reference large files (huge.fastq.gz, etc.)
# that are not included. This script demonstrates the streaming
# API using the included sample data.

